  33:verify.c      **** * Name:        PQCLEAN_MLKEM512_CLEAN_cmov
  34:verify.c      **** *
  35:verify.c      **** * Description: Copy len bytes from x to r if b is 1;
  36:verify.c      **** *              don't modify x if b is 0. Requires b to be in {0,1};
  37:verify.c      **** *              assumes two's complement representation of negative integers.
  38:verify.c      **** *              Runs in constant time.
